<item>
            <title>[AVRO-2058] ReflectData#isNonStringMap returns true for Utf8 keys</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-2058</link>
                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since &lt;tt&gt;Utf8&lt;/tt&gt; does not have an &lt;tt&gt;Stringable&lt;/tt&gt; notation, and is not in &lt;tt&gt;SpecificData#stringableClasses&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;ReflectData#isNonStringMap&lt;/tt&gt; returns true. This also causes &lt;tt&gt;ReflectData#isArray&lt;/tt&gt; to return true for maps with Utf8 keys, and thus &lt;tt&gt;GenericData#resolveUnion&lt;/tt&gt; fails as well. This ultimately causes &lt;tt&gt;ReflectData#write&lt;/tt&gt; to fail for schemas that contain a union that contains a map, where the data uses Utf8 for strings.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This following test case reproduces the issue:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;  @Test &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void testUnionWithMapWithUtf8Keys() {
    Schema s = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Schema.Parser().parse
      (&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;[\&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;\&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;, {\&quot;&lt;/span&gt;type\&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;:\&quot;&lt;/span&gt;map\&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;,\&quot;&lt;/span&gt;values\&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;:\&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;float&lt;/span&gt;\&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;}]&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
    GenericData data = ReflectData.get();
    HashMap&amp;lt;Utf8,&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Float&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; map = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; HashMap&amp;lt;Utf8,&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Float&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;();
    map.put(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Utf8(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 1.0f);
    assertEquals(1, data.resolveUnion(s, map));
  }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
